<surface xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:sga="http://shelleygodwinarchive.org/ns/1.0" ulx="0" uly="0"
  lrx="5406" lry="7276" xml:id="ox-ms_shelley_e1-0028" partOf="#ox-ms_shelley_e1">
  <graphic url="http://shelleygodwinarchive.org/images/ox/ox-ms_shelley_e1-0028.jp2"/>
  <zone type="main">
    <line rend="indent1">All things confess his strength&#x2014;<mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">From the cold mass</del>
        <add place="sublinear">Through the cold mass</add>
      </mod></line>
    <line rend="indent1">Of marble &amp; of colour his dreams pass</line>
    <line><mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">And Mothers gazing</del>
        <add place="superlinear">Bright threads, whence mothers</add>
      </mod> weave the robes their children wear;</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Language is a perpetual Orphic song</line>
    <line><mod>
        <add place="intralinear">Ruling</add>
        <del rend="strikethrough">Which rules</del>
      </mod> with d&#xE6;dal harmony, <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">the</del>
        <add place="superlinear">a</add>
      </mod> throng</line>
    <line>Of thoughts &amp; forms, which else senseless &amp; shapeless were</line>
    <line rend="indent1">The Lightning is his slave; Heavens utmost deep</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Gives up her stars, &amp; like a flock of sheep</line>
    <line>They pass before his eye, are numbered, &amp; roll on!</line>
    <line rend="indent1">The Tempest is his steed,&#x2014;he strides the air!</line>
    <line rend="indent1"><milestone unit="tei:l" spanTo="#e1-0028.01"/>And the abyss shouts from her
      depth</line>
    <line rend="right">laid bare<anchor xml:id="e1-0028.01"/></line>
    <line><del rend="unmarked" instant="true">Wh</del><del rend="strikethrough" instant="true">at
        secrets hast thou Heaven</del><del instant="true" rend="ummarked">?</del></line>
    <line><milestone unit="tei:l" spanTo="#e1-0028.02"/>Heaven, hast thou secrets? Man unveils me,
      I</line>
    <line rend="right">have none<anchor xml:id="e1-0028.02"/></line>
    <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e1-0028.05"/>
    <line rend="center">The Moon</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e1-0028.05"/>
    <line rend="indent1">The shadow of white Death hath past</line>
    <line rend="indent1">From my path in Heaven at last,</line>
    <line>A clinging shroud of solid frost &amp; sleep&#x2014;</line>
    <line rend="indent1">And through my newly-woven bowers</line>
  </zone>
</surface>
